abstract: Bill Haas takes one-stroke victory at Humana Challenge in La Quinta, Calif; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Haas pulled ahead with a 20-foot birdie putt on the par-4 16th hole and parred the final two holes for a one-stroke victory at the Humana Challenge in La Quinta, Calif.
